
First go to Apache lounge official website ,download the binary file,Extract the zip file,

There will be 3 options visible click on Apache24 then go inside this folder ,search the conf folder inside this folder you will find httpd file open this file in notepad...
and minimize this now open Apache24 folder and copy this path (C:/Users/Apache24) and go in notepad you will find SV ROOT="GIVE YOU PATH HERE..." save the changes.

Now go to Apache24 folder inside that bin folder open cmd in this path C:/Users/Apache24/bin> ./httpd.exe ----------now enter after writting this allow access.

Then open any browswer and type localhost 
If it shows It Works

Great JOB!!!!!
